===Etymology===
From {{der|en|la|abacus}}, {{m|la|abax}}; from {{der|en|grc|ἄβαξ||board covered with sand}}, possibly from a {{der|en|sem}} source; compare {{cog|he|אבק||dust|tr=āvāq}}.

